name: voucherEntryProceedToPayment

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged in to Voucher Entry page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Accounts Payable,Voucher Entries,Voucher Entry}

testSteps.description: Then the Payment Information form and its contents should show up
When I set the Supplier to '133339'
When I set the 'Invoice Number' to 'QtNbSLBhQa'
When I set the Currency to 'USD'
When i click on continue button
When I select the first Bank Account and click 'Submit' button if modal exist
When I set the Gross Amount to '15000'
When I set the Payment Terms to '30'
When I set the Tax Area to 'KF7'

children.description: When i click the last payment amount table row if its not editable

testSteps.description: Then the tax amount of the first line should be filled out
When i click on continue button
Then the 'GL Distribution' form and its contents should show up
When I fill up the last row line and balance the amount using Account Number: '91100', Line Description: 'Test', Cost Center: '1MAN400', Gen Obj: 'AFGHAI', AOE: 'YAO', Line Ref: 'Test1'

children.description: When I click the last 'Additional Lines' table row
When I set the 'Account Number' to '91100'
When I set the 'Line Description' to 'Test'
When I set the 'Cost Center' to '1MAN400'
When I set the 'Gen Obj' to 'AFGHAI'
When I click on 'Show Next' button
When I click on 'Show Previous' button

testSteps.description: When I click on 'Save' button
Then the voucher entry successfully created modal and its contents should show up

children.description: Then the voucher entry successfully created modal should show up
Then the batch number from voucher entry successfully created modal should show up
Then the document number from voucher entry successfully created modal should show up

testSteps.description: When i click on proceed to payment button
Then that 'Manual Payment' page and its contents should show up
Then the saved invoice should be selected
When I click the 'Select Cash' button
Then the 'Select Cash Account' modal should show up
When I select the first account from 'Select cash account' modal
When I click the 'Submit' button from modal
When I click on 'Proceed' button
Then the 'Manual Payment Successfully Created' modal should show up

children.description: Then the manual payment successfully created modal should show up

exception.message: Expected condition failed: waiting for visibility of element located by By.xpath: //div[contains(@class, 'modal') and contains(@style, 'left: 0px')]//h3 (tried for 20 second(s) with 100 milliseconds interval)

children.description: Then the batch number should be displayed in manual payment successfully created modal
Then the payment number should be displayed in manual payment successfully created modal
